name: MISS SOCIAL BOOTCAMP
description:
The DETAILS: 
Are you an entrepreneur who wants to ROCK your business? 
Seriously, need help getting your business SOCIAL?  Do you want a killer online marketing strategy? On top of that, have any desire to hang with a group of people just like yourself, all who want to see, learn and take their business to the next level?
Ya. You do. 

The MISS SOCIAL BOOTCAMP 
is a 2 day business marathon. And it goes like this…
•	We will dive in to an all systems check of your website 
        and how to make it work for your business. 
•	We’ll Badass your Facebook+Pinterest Social Media accounts. 
•	Most important, we will discuss the approach behind it all. 

         You will be a marketing ROCKSTAR when it’s all over.
 
How to make your business do what you want it to do… make cash and be successful, hello! 

Most important, this is going to be fun. 
Think:
•	good eats
•	good music 
•	great people 
paired with all the stuff you wanna know for your business. 
It’s gonna be awesome. 

The LOGISTICS:
You’ll need: 
•	A laptop
•	A business 
•	Travel & overnight arrangements 

What’s Included: 
•	A full fledged 2 day workshop for your business
•	A delish lunch 
•	A BADASS SOCIAL goody bag

Limited to 25 Participants.
Booking for January NYC+Connecticut
